  "title": "Monopolist shown on graph will exit in long run",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><include href=\"../Passage/VR023901.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following will the firm do in the long run if market conditions do not change?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It will increase output to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 2\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>Q</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and lower price to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P sub 2\"><math alttext=\"P sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to minimize losses.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It will increase output to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 3\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>Q</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and raise price to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P sub 4\"><math alttext=\"P sub 4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to earn zero economic profit.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It will produce <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 1\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>Q</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and set price equal to marginal revenue.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It will exit the industry.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It will build a larger plant to achieve decreasing returns to scale.</p>",
        "value": "i5"
      }
    ]
  },
